  <title>Create a new file</title>

  <p>
    The easiest way to create a new file in <app>gedit</app> is to click the
    <gui>Create a new document</gui> button on the left side of the header bar.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you have other files open in <app>gedit</app>, the new file that you
    create will appear as a new tab to the right of those files.
  </p>
